{"tid":794452,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"教學 簡單煮羊架大法","createTime":"2018-08-26T09:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T05:24:29.000Z","uid":105604,"like":22,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"57addb4976d31fbb24e12beb08af42ae8770f670","tid":794452,"uid":105604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"屋企有咩調味料都落曬去，大量，要多到見唔到羊架本新個樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/163017_85e6e0ebd738ddec7f51edc20ba03309.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F163017_85e6e0ebd738ddec7f51edc20ba03309.png&h=d4fb5981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放啲食得既野係個底到，例如琴晚食剩既餸，一陣啲羊汁留落去就會變得勁好食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/163243_10fff0cf66ddd50dedee9e65d2b0a3f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F163243_10fff0cf66ddd50dedee9e65d2b0a3f8.png&h=79d50049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/163447_154bebad028c6c656fba0c4e35b993c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F163447_154bebad028c6c656fba0c4e35b993c3.png&h=914ccedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥皂向上230度五分鐘，180度三分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/163505_6b4e0e76effa976fe77af39269062318.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F163505_6b4e0e76effa976fe77af39269062318.png&h=0fece1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反轉佢，180度再焗8分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/163909_9bdc3d4ce2c8ee89f8b26423fbc9edcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F163909_9bdc3d4ce2c8ee89f8b26423fbc9edcf.png&h=1773d4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再反轉，180度4分鐘，五成熟！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/164626_f33c1248ae7d4c9558af81829f867734.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F164626_f33c1248ae7d4c9558af81829f867734.png&h=5ced0c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這樣，再加石紙四分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/165245_b12cd9d6de06a32b4ca55458faa2c448.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F165245_b12cd9d6de06a32b4ca55458faa2c448.png&h=14b276df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這樣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/165323_314871aeb49c1fd8d16027037cfb1418.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F165323_314871aeb49c1fd8d16027037cfb1418.png&h=60bb08ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🤤🤤🤤🤤<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/170220_1ccaddabdff8dac755d6a6270b1ac727.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F170220_1ccaddabdff8dac755d6a6270b1ac727.png&h=dc06d616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/170224_ca1b918acdac2c2bae0c12dd66f08b9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F170224_ca1b918acdac2c2bae0c12dd66f08b9f.png&h=99469ba6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bb0218cd87b380d585900f097a0fccc2044fb86","tid":794452,"uid":31029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f7680deaa0e23e994b31e1ca8df2e03773ec24f0","tid":794452,"uid":15754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"d3670f08b59c092af27a3d4e6e2f07450daf0f89","tid":794452,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0